Name: OpenMRS ID
Description: Medical Record Number generated by OpenMRS for every patient

Name: Legacy ID
Description: Identifier type to record optional previous identifers

Name: SSN
Format description: Identifier should be 1 letter, followed by a dash and 7 numerical characters. Eg, A-0010902

Name: Unique OPD Number
Description: Record the unique OPD number which is given to each NEW out patient  annually and on the first visit for individual identification
